{"word":"Andrew","slug":"andrew","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Andrew</b> - the apostle<p/><b>(1)</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=18'>Mat 4:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=29'>Mar 1:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=13&verse=3'>Mar 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=40'>Joh 1:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=8'>Joh 6:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=22'>Joh 12:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a><p/><b>(2) \"A Personal Worker\"</b><p/>Brother of Peter<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=18'>Mt 4:18</a><p/>Originally a disciple of John the Baptist<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=35'>Joh 1:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=40'>Joh 1:40</a><p/>Spent a day in Christ's home<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=39'>Joh 1:39</a><p/>Responded immediately when called<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=19'>Mat 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=20'>Mat 4:20</a><p/>Brought Peter to Christ<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=42'>Joh 1:42</a><p/>Prompt to help<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=8'>Joh 6:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=9'>Joh 6:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=21'>Joh 12:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=22'>Joh 12:22</a>"}]}